INSERT INTO `travel_note` VALUES ('5', '24', '主题旅行案列', '造访神眷顾的土地，接受心灵的洗礼：徒步雅拉雪山，穿行甲居藏寨归来', '雅拉雪山 甲居藏寨 川西 旅游 雪山 心灵之旅 摄影之旅', '雅拉雪山 甲居藏寨 川西 旅游 雪山 心灵之旅 摄影之旅', '<p>\n <img src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/images/1341994241_IGP8484_e_.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n <strong>时间：</strong> 2009.08.11-2009.08.15<br />\n<strong>行程：</strong> 成都--二郎山--康定--雅拉雪山--丹巴--成都<br />\n<br />\n雅拉雪山，藏语全称为“夏学雅拉嘎波”（意为东方白牦牛山），系中国藏区四大神山之一。位于四川甘孜州康定、道孚和丹巴三县的交界处，海拔5884米，与它西北方向的墨尔多神山遥遥相对。山顶终年积雪，是康巴地区一座著名的神山，雅拉河即发源于此。在雅拉神山4000多米的山腰处，有两个相距不到300米的两个海子，他们的出水方向分别朝南北方向流入山脊的两面。形成了一道靓丽的自然景观。<br />\n甲居,藏语的本意是指“百户人家”。甲居藏寨位于四川甘孜州丹巴县境内，距县城约8公里，犹如田园牧歌般的童话世界，享有“藏区童话世界”的美称。\n</p>\n<p>\n 告别暄嚣的城市，去那宁静的天空寻找梦的起点，放飞自己....... <br />\n让我们在溪流旁品味山泉的甘洌，在夜里用心去感触星空，听夜在耳边低吟......<br />\n我们想要的是不仅仅是生命的长度，更重要的是我们在乎它的深度......&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n闭上眼睛,山谷就是我们的胸怀,涌动的云雾就是自己的心潮,而耳边流动的就是那自由与爱的声音......&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n兴许这里就是人间与天堂的交汇处,美在这里延续,生命在这里轮回,而我们,在这里感动…… &nbsp;<br />\n为什么我们要浪迹天涯,因为,我们的灵魂在寻找家乡........\n</p>\n<p>\n <img src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713104118_DSC_0172.JPG.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 出发啦，不要问那路在哪儿，迎风向前，是唯一的方法……\n</p>\n<p>\n <img src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713104252_DSC_0174.JPG.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 著名的二郎山隧道，使川藏线上的天堑变通途\n</p>\n<p>\n <img src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712120016_DSC_3405.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 花开正艳，似要把大地染色\n</p>\n<p>\n <img src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712114515__IGP8324.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 草木皆情\n</p>\n<p>\n <img src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712114616__IGP8401.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 营地午餐\n</p>\n<p>\n <img src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712114540__IGP8399.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 自己动手，丰衣足食\n</p>\n<p>\n <img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713104750__IGP8482修改.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 这算是叠罗汉么？\n</p>\n<p>\n <img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713104815__IGP8483修改.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n pose一定要摆够<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713104829__IGP8589.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 躺在雪山下，感受太阳神的恩惠<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713104853_DSC_0446.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713104928_DSC_0475.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n <img src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713110033_DSC_0455.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n <img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713110339_DSC_0489.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713110342_DSC_3446.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713110344_DSC_3460.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713110521_DSC_0497.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713110527_DSC_0527.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 湖水明如镜，云朵白如棉<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713110532_DSC_0560.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713110535_DSC_0605.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713110544_DSC_0621.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 唯美景色<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713110549_DSC_0633.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 骑着登山杖去旅行，飞吧！<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713110557_DSC_3815.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 碧波万顷\n</p>\n<p>\n <img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713110848_DSC_0664.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 在这里仰望天堂<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713110851_DSC_3805.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 神山<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713110853_DSC_3844.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> &nbsp; <img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713110856_DSC_3846.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 大哥，你这宾得广告做得好&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 在神山神湖前虔诚祈祷<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713111052_DSC_0701.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 路旁向日葵<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713111057_DSC_0746.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 甲居藏寨\n</p>\n<p>\n <img src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713111122_DSC_4217.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 落脚的地儿，当地特色藏居\n</p>\n<p>\n <img src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713111502_090811雅拉徒步25.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 藏居内部，浓烈的民族风装饰<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713111100_DSC_0748.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713111101_DSC_0781.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 摘果子，好欢乐！&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 晚餐<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713111106_DSC_0796.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 队员们与我们领队合影<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713111109_DSC_0809.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 八美，莲花之地<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713111114_DSC_0831.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 青稞渐黄\n</p>\n<p>\n <br />\n</p>', '小螃蟹', '2012-07-13', '2009.08.11 - 2009.08.15', '/utoadmin/uploads/images/1341994241_IGP8484_e_.jpg');
INSERT INTO `travel_note` VALUES ('6', '24', '主题旅行案列', '春光轻柔，有暗香盈袖：金川·丹巴赏梨花归来 ', '梨花 金川 丹巴 川西 旅游', '梨花 金川 丹巴 川西 旅游', '<p>\n <img src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/images/1341992921DSC_0522.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 活动时间：2012.03.19—2012.03.25\n</p>\n<p>\n 活动路线：成都—米亚罗—马尔康—金川—丹巴—中路—丹巴—甲居藏寨—泸定—成都\n</p>\n<p>\n “雪梨之乡”金川：横断山区的大金川峡谷中，是内地联系西藏、青海、甘肃等藏族地区的桥梁和咽喉。每到春季河两岸嫩绿的垂柳迎风招展，峡谷里，山坡上散落着粉红的桃花、晶莹的梨花、橙黄的油菜花，一派春意盎然。\n</p>\n<p>\n <span< p=\"\"></span<>\n</p>\n<p>\n <span< p=\"\"></span<>\n</p>\n<p>\n <span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712153106_DSC_0448.jpg.jpg\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 羌藏风情\n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712153120_DSC_0411.jpg.jpg\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 碉楼\n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712153140_DSC_0466.jpg.jpg\" />那些树枝纷披的梨树上缀满花朵，仿佛是飘着大片的雪花。\n</p>\n<p>\n <span< p=\"\"></span<>\n</p>\n<p>\n <span< p=\"\"></span<>\n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712153156_DSC_0469.jpg.jpg\" />风夹着梨花的馨香，在树旁枝尾悠悠飘荡，人吸一口，心都醉了。\n</p>\n<p>\n <span< p=\"\"></span<>\n</p>\n<p>\n <span< p=\"\"></span<>\n</p>\n<p>\n <span< p=\"\"></span<>\n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712153230_DSC_0499.jpg.jpg\" />古朴碉楼与洁白梨花相辉映\n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712153257_DSC_0500.jpg.jpg\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 空气中氤氲着淡淡的梨花的香甜气息，扑人肺腑，使人像喝醉了醇酒，轻飘飘，晕乎乎的。\n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712153339_DSC_0511.jpg.jpg\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 那些梨花，密密匝匝，层层叠叠，如白云轻飘，如雪花漫洒，满枝，满树，满园。\n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712153355_DSC_0513.jpg.jpg\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 正是梨树花开的时节，银白如雪的花朵衬托得这农家小院分外的热闹\n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712153433_DSC_0525.jpg.jpg\" />羌族的老妈妈们跳起了民族舞舞蹈\n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712153451_DSC_0535.jpg.jpg\" />“一柱擎天”的马尔邦关碉\n</p>\n<p>\n <em></em><em>中国碉王——马尔邦关碉，高达49.8米，基宽6.5×5米，顶宽3米，是目前已知保存较好的古碉，被誉为“中国碉王”迄今已有近300多年的历史，为原大金川土司莎罗奔的小官寨碉。</em><em></em> \n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712153513_DSC_0543.jpg.jpg\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 远眺，村里村外，山上山下，密密麻麻的梨花融成了一片白茫茫的花海，连山野都被逮住了。\n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712153532_DSC_0548.jpg.jpg\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 簇簇闪光的梨花，酷似那江上的朵朵雪浪。\n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712153547_DSC_0550.jpg.jpg\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 雪白雪白的梨花挂满枝头，微风拂过，宛如穿着缟素的玉女翩翩起舞。\n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712153630_DSC_0561.jpg.jpg\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 远处看梨花，树密花稠，加上一江春水，好似看一幅重笔浓彩的油画，浓郁、热烈。\n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712153648_DSC_0558.jpg.jpg\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 油菜花也开了，缤纷的色彩渲染着大地\n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712153711_DSC_0566.JPG.jpg\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 队员们在羌民家进餐\n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712153735_DSC_0579.jpg.jpg\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 甲居藏寨\n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712153755_DSC_0589.jpg.jpg\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 绿油油的梯田，\n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712153818_DSC_0616.jpg.jpg\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 好专业\n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712153839_DSC_0612.jpg.jpg\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 大姐在换上民族服饰后显得格外欣喜\n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712153910_DSC_0651.jpg.jpg\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 打情骂俏哟\n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712154022_DSC_0639.jpg.jpg\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 多个爱的小妹妹！\n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712154142_DSC_0657.jpg.jpg\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712154206_DSC_0688.jpg.jpg\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 山坡上，一片片雪白的梨花、嫩红的桃花，在阳光里流泻着醉人的色彩。\n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712154239_DSC_0702.jpg.jpg\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712154256_DSC_0716.jpg.jpg\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 在近处看梨花，树稀花疏，好似看一幅轻笔淡墨的山水画，清淡、恬雅。\n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712155403_DSC_0724.jpg.jpg\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712155430_DSC_0730.jpg.jpg\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712155455_DSC_0741.jpg.jpg\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712155506_DSC_0751.jpg.jpg\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712155519_DSC_0781.jpg.jpg\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712155532_DSC_0810.jpg.jpg\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712155545_DSC_0841.jpg.jpg\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712155617_DSC_0822.jpg.jpg\" />\n</p>\n<p>\n 喜夺泸定桥\n</p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712155626_DSC_0832.jpg.jpg\" />\n</p>\n<p>\n 掷弹手<br />\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712155634_DSC_0857.jpg.jpg\" />\n</p>\n<p>\n 队员和我们领队玩儿雪<br />\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120712155639_DSC_0858.jpg.jpg\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 二郎山隧道，隧道两头冰火两重天\n</p>', '小螃蟹', '2012-07-13', '2012.03.19—2012.03.25', '/utoadmin/uploads/images/1341992921DSC_0522.jpg');
INSERT INTO `travel_note` VALUES ('7', '25', '主题旅行案列', '造访上帝的颜料库——新都桥、稻城、亚丁三神山9日游归来', '川西 旅游 新都桥 稻城亚丁 三神山 摄影 心灵之旅', '川西 旅游 新都桥 稻城亚丁 三神山 摄影 心灵之旅', '<p>\n <img src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/images/1341992672_o_A2.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 活动时间：2011.10.09-2011.10.17<br />\n活动线路：成都--二郎山--新都桥--理塘--稻城--亚丁--五色海/牛奶海--稻城--新都桥--八美--丹巴--成都<br />\n<br />\n稻城亚丁沉睡在岁月的冰河，方圆7323平方公里的土地存留着大地最古老的记忆和大自然最真最纯的心灵。它被时光遗忘，千万年来，日升日落，默默地守着自己旷世的美景。<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 最早发现稻城亚丁的是美国传教士约瑟夫.洛克，1928年, 他从云南丽江出发，经四川木里县到达稻城，并把所拍到的照片发表在美国《国家地理杂志》上，引起了巨大轰动，但他当时并未发现他到的是稻城，而一直认为是云南中甸。直到1996年, 有关专家才确认洛克所到之地“香格里拉”乃稻城亚丁。　　<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 稻城亚丁的北部是青藏高原最大的古冰遗迹——海子山自然保护区，自然景观旷远、原始、混沌。稻城亚丁的中部是开阔的河谷、草原、牧草丰茂，鲜花飘香。它的南部是连绵不断、千姿百态的山峰，深谷幽坚，湍流飞瀑。尤为著名的是驰名藏区的念青贡嘎日松布露峰和它神秘的传说。　<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 最重要的是稻城亚丁拥有最纯的生灵，傲视天穹的神鹰，自由生活的各种野生动物，草场林间婉转歌唱的鸟儿，静静地放牧着自己的牧人。稻城亚丁，有你能够想到的一切，也有你想象之外的一切。\n</p>\n<p>\n <img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713121646_泸定桥.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />大渡桥横铁索寒\n</p>\n<p>\n <img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713121659_折多山2.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />康巴第一关：折多山口<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713121623_理塘.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n悬在高空的城市——理塘<br />\n由成都去稻城，理塘是必经之地。<br />\n理塘，藏语叫“勒通”，意为平坦如铜镜似的草原。自古便是茶马互市的重镇，商贾云集，物华天宝，人杰地灵。享有“草原明珠”之称。是康巴藏民族的聚居地。四千多米的海拔亦使它享有“世界高城”之称，县城比西藏拉萨还要高300多米。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713121636_理塘到稻城路边1.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713121851_理塘到稻城路边.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713115017_DSC_0563.JPG.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713121814_稻城3.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713121826_稻城6.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713121802_稻城1.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713121810_稻城2.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713121843_稻城9.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<div <br=\"\">\n </div>\n <p>\n  <img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713140943_DSC_0130.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713140950_DSC_0162.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713141004_冲古寺3.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n </p>\n <p>\n  冲古寺位于仙乃日雪峰脚下，隶属贡嘎朗吉岭寺，根戈活佛派有扎巴在此念经颂佛，小经堂内供有泥塑释迦。在老寺庙旁建有一个二层房屋，有一个喇嘛负责管理过往旅客的入住（现在由于景区规定，很难再住进去）及保护周围生态环境。一层为客房及喇嘛房间，二层为经堂，游人不能上二楼。每日早上及下午喇嘛都要熏香念经，每当这时诵经声和法豉声在寂静的山谷中回响，使这里显得更加神圣和神秘。\n </p>\n <p>\n  <img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713140957_冲古寺2.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp; <img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713141013_洛绒牛场4.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713141011_洛绒牛场3.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713141020_夏诺多吉雪山4.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713141031_亚丁1.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713141034_亚丁2.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp; <img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713141038_亚丁3.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713141043_亚丁4.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n </p>\n <p>\n  彩虹高挂<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713141048_亚丁5.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n </p>\n <p>\n  半山上寺院<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713141055_亚丁6.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713141100_亚丁7.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713141105_珍珠海1.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713141450_亚丁.JPG.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n </p>', '小螃蟹', '2012-07-13', '2011.10.09-2011.10.17', '/utoadmin/uploads/images/1341992672_o_A2.jpg');
INSERT INTO `travel_note` VALUES ('8', '24', '友途活动案例', '端午特别定制团：徒步双桥沟，勇攀四姑娘山二峰！', '四姑娘山 双桥沟 二峰 攀登 徒步 川西 旅游', '四姑娘山 双桥沟 二峰 攀登 徒步 川西 旅游', '<p>\n <img src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713145426_1.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n 【活动时间】2012年6月21-25日<br />\n【活动线路】成都-水磨镇-映秀-日隆镇-四姑娘山（长坪沟-海子沟二峰）--成都<br />\n【活动主办】成都友途旅行网<br />\n【活动领队】木灯<br />\n【回顾图文】友途小编<br />\n【活动简介】端午特别策划四姑娘山二峰攀登的经典完美线路组合，特别定制的旅行计划，行程安排合理，适合身体<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; 健康体能充沛的普通旅游爱好者以及初级入门的户外爱好者，充分感受深度纯净高原旅游的乐趣，圆自<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; 己的攀登雪山的梦想<br />\n【行程安排】第一天：成都—水墨镇—映秀地震遗址—日隆镇<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 第二天：日隆镇—双桥沟—日隆镇<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 第三天：日隆镇—二峰大本营（海子沟）<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; 第四天：二峰大本营—二峰峰顶—二峰大本营—日隆镇<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; 第五天：日隆镇—成都\n</p>\n<p>\n ------------------------------------------------------- 我是华丽的分界线-------------------------------------------------\n</p>\n<p>\n 6月21日，初夏，成都。8位来自广东的朋友，在友途的带领下开始了对四姑娘山二峰的征程。\n</p>\n<p>\n <img src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713145429_2.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713145433_3.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n&nbsp;临行前我们的领队把为此行的队友们采购回的干粮零食都分装、打包好。各种零食，眼馋不？<img src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713145439_4.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />为队员们准备的头巾\n</p>\n<p>\n 上午11点左右，队员们到达水磨镇。水磨镇地处阿坝州汶川县南部岷江支流寿溪河畔，距世界文化遗产古迹都江堰市仅34公里。在5.12地震中曾遭到重大损失，地震后重新修建，一半是汉民族风格的禅寿老街，另一半是羌族风格浓郁的羌城。\n</p>\n<p>\n <img src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713145448_5.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />广东省佛山市对口援建水磨镇，根据规划，水磨被打造成为了独具羌族特色的旅游小镇<img src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713145456_7.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />极具羌族特色的民饰<img src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713145502_8.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />绿树掩映中漂亮的羌族民居\n</p>\n<p>\n 下午1点过，队员们到达映秀地震遗址\n</p>\n<p>\n <img src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713145508_10.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />我们的8位队员与领队木灯（左一）<img src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713145512_11.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />在地震遗址稍作停留之后，我们继续向四姑娘山挺进。\n</p>\n<p>\n <img src=\"/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713145521_13.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />沿途野花烂漫<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150557_14.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />恩爱的一对儿\n</p>\n<p>\n 下午5点左右抵达四姑娘山脚下的日隆镇<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150601_15.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />非常可口且地道的晚餐<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150605_16.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />开饭了，开饭了，右下的大哥别发微博了\n</p>\n<p>\n 经过一夜休整，队员们个个精神饱满，队伍于9点半进入双桥沟景区。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150608_21.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />这一刻，沉醉于大自然的气息<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150612_22.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />经幡、白塔、远山、白云，圣洁而旷远<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150618_25.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />队员们饿坏了<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150623_26.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />我们为队员们搭建了天幕，以供队员们避雨休息。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150628_27.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />天放晴，队员们来劲了，四下活动开来<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150631_28.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />你跳的有我高吗？<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150638_31.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />飞起来了！<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150643_34.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />巴扎嘿……<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150650_36.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />泰坦“石”克号，浪漫哟！<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150653_37.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />夏花烂漫，白云舒卷，青山排挞，天境湛蓝。恍惚间似天宫佳境，回首望却在人间。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150659_39.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />在此间瑜伽，与自然一体，何等享受！<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150705_40.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />见有人带领，大家都开始练瑜伽。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150711_42.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />千手观音，哈哈哈哈<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150715_43.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />手拉手，肩并肩，我们一同看蓝天。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150723_44.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />美女一时兴起，表演江湖中失传已久的武林绝学：佛山无影脚<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150730_45.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />曼妙的舞姿，芭蕾有木有！<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150735_46.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />就这样依偎在你怀里，看山花如何变黄，看白云如何飘远。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150834_47.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />你是天上的一片云，偶而投在我的湖心<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150840_48.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />人在画中游<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150843_49.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;路遇油菜花田，果断停车拍照\n</p>\n<p>\n 队员们于下午6点返回了日隆镇休整。\n</p>\n<p>\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150846_52.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />23日的早餐。端午节，粽子必须有！<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150850_53.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />吃过早餐，队员们开始朝二峰大本营进发！<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150855_54.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />路开始变得不好走，但终于摆脱了钢筋水泥的快乐该如何言表？<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150859_55.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />遥望山峰，美不甚收<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150903_56.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />原木的指示牌显得特别和谐<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150910_57.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />莫愁前路无知己，天涯何人不识君<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150913_58.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />一路绿草同行，山花为伴<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150922_59.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />跋涉中……<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150924_60.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />终于抵达了大本营\n</p>\n<p>\n 俗话说计划总赶不上变化快，23日当晚4名队员因为身体原选择放弃登顶，而24日凌晨3点半起床后不久临时又有两位队员退出，木灯和两位协作带上剩余的两位队员过客和画出彩虹在4点30开始出发。但出发不到半小时，队员画出彩虹出现头痛、呼吸困难的症状、为了安全考虑，也尊重当事人的选择，我们安排了其中一名协作陪同其返回大本营，木灯和另一位协作带着唯一的队员过客继续前进，护送画出彩虹的协作在完成护送任务后，追赶上我们，队伍最终是四人<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713150926_61.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />拂晓，天色微明。山峰在霞光映衬下显得格外秀丽。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713151023_62.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />协作之一<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713151028_63.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713151033_64.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />唯一参与登顶的队员过客在领队和协作的帮助下前行着<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713151038_65.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />攀登途中遇上日照金山<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713151041_66.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />继续前行，碎石坡阻挡不了前进的步伐<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713151045_67.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />回望来路<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713151046_68.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />翻山越岭，不只是为风景，还为一颗挑战自己的心。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713151048_70.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />有云海涌动<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713151053_71.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />看着脚下前人的脚印，我们并不孤独<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713151055_72.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />群峰迤逦<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713151059_73.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />登顶成功！<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713151103_74.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />OH!YEAH!!<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713151107_76.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />遥遥相望的四姑娘山三峰<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713151108_78.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />不畏浮云遮望眼，只缘身在最高层<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713151113_79.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />开始起雾了，为了安全，即刻下撤<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713151115_80.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />下撤途中<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713151116_81.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />我们的协作和队员。嗯，领队呢？额……正在拍照 <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713151121_82.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />尽职尽责的协作，让队员的安全有了可靠保障<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713151128_83.jpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" />碎石坡上的红景天\n</p>\n<p>\n ------------------------------------------------------- 我是华丽的分界线-------------------------------------------------\n</p>\n<p>\n 山峰简介 <br />\n四姑娘山二峰海拔5276米，由日隆镇海子沟口至二峰峰顶，全程大至为24公里山路，上升绝对高度为2100米以上，沿途水源补给充足，整条路线没有险要地段。一般气候下：二峰12月至5月有6个月的积雪期，夏秋间的7至11月没有积雪，由于二峰与大部分雪山比较其雪线较短，海拔相对较低，体能要求仅标准级（前提是身体状况正常，无高原反应），对冰雪技术的要求也不高，所以成为登山爱好者攀登初级雪山的入门级绝好场所。\n</p>\n<p>\n 气候状况<br />\n四姑娘山区地处中亚热带季风气候向大陆性高原气候过渡地区，由于高原地形，气候冬寒夏凉，常年干燥，雨量稀少，年降水量1100-1600毫升，降水主要集中在雨季（5月），山地自然垂直带谱很有代表性。且气温变化剧烈，四季不甚明显，日温差较大，有时达20C以上。年蒸发量1500毫米，无霜期220天，年平均气温12.2°C，全年光照2214小时。<br />\n四姑娘山是典型的高原气候，早晚凉，中午热，蓝天白云，晚上星光灿烂，空气新鲜，但由于海拨高，部份人会有程度不同的高山反应。绝好场所。\n</p>\n<p>\n 游客咨询<br />\n问：此次雪山攀登的海拔高度？<br />\n答：四姑娘山二峰海拔5454米。<br />\n问：四姑娘山二峰适合普通人攀登吗？对个人的户外技能要求高吗？<br />\n答：我们不建议没有一点户外常识的普通人攀登四姑娘山二峰。因为相对于大峰，二峰攀登难度更大一些。更适合身体健康体能充沛具有一定户外知识及经验的初级入门的户外爱好者。<br />\n问：如果我们没有装备，可以参加活动吗？<br />\n答：所有徒步露营攀登需要的专业装备都由我们提供，在这一点上朋友们不用担心。\n</p>', '小螃蟹', '2012-07-13', '2012.06.21-2012.06.25', '/utoadmin/uploads/routeimg/20120713145426_1.jpg.jpg');
INSERT INTO `travel_note` VALUES ('9', '24', '友途活动案例', '体验藏家风情，感受川西美景：新都桥、泉华滩、折多山、雅家埂5日游', '', '', '<p>\n <img alt=\"\" img=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/images/DSC_4595.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" img=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/images/DSC_4657(1).jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n <img alt=\"\" img=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/images/DSC_4681.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" img=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/images/DSC_4696.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" img=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/images/DSC_4729.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/images/DSC_4746.jpg\"  720px; height: 482px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/images/DSC_4748.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/images/DSC_4752.JPG\"  720px; height: 468px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/images/DSC_4756.jpg\"  720px; height: 482px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/images/DSC_4750.JPG\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/images/DSC_4757.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/images/DSC_4712.JPG\"  720px; height: 482px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/images/P1110677.jpg\"  720px; height: 481px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/images/DSC_4809.jpg\"  720px; height: 482px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/images/pgwikmnhkjslxrtsx.jpg\"  720px; height: 480px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/images/DSC_4819.jpg\"  720px; height: 482px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/images/DSC_4823.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/images/DSC_4832.jpg\"  720px; height: 482px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/images/pgwikmnhkjslxrts.jpg\"  720px; height: 480px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/images/DSC_4848_1.jpg\"  720px; height: 590px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/images/DSC_4867.jpg\"  720px; height: 482px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/images/DSC_4862.jpg\"  720px; height: 482px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/images/DSC_4871.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/images/DSC_4891.jpg\"  720px; height: 482px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/images/DSC_4893.jpg\"  720px; height: 482px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/images/DSC_4886(1).JPG\"  720px; height: 1076px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/images/DSC_4944.jpg\"  720px; height: 414px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/images/DSC_4952.jpg\"  720px; height: 482px;\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/images/DSC_4940.jpg\" /></p>\n', '小螃蟹', '2012-07-13', '2012.06.20-2012.06.24', 'http://www.utotrip.com/utoadmin/uploads/images/DSC_4595.jpg');

